<L>__{exterior river magua night}
<A>__{beaches a canoe on the bank. he and eight braves ease out. his war paint is fresh: green handprints on his chest and black and green on his face. black plumes are affixed to his scalp lock and his shawl is over his left shoulder. the right arm carrying his musket is exposed. many scalps are tied to his tomahawk. he walks towards us approaching the island, two hundred yards away ...}
